{"id":432191,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":6,"day":24}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"237","ytitle":"","mtitle":"表的颂歌","ftitle":"","authors":["郑成义"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑成义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小的螺丝钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小的，草绿的机床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梳妆台一样清净、明亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面镜子一盏灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台前坐着一个女工。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀具，象蝴蝶在轻搧翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机声，象蜜蜂在轻轻弹唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油管里喷吐着你的心血——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺丝钉小得象砂粒一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你，你看得多么准确，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的岗位，正象一颗螺丝钉一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间，在每一颗螺丝钉上前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，在每一颗螺丝钉上成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装钻石的工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你头也不抬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼也不<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1962\\06\\626o0406AA.JPG\">，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针尖上挑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小的红星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一秒钟，十颗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红光光，亮晶晶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几时才嵌满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的满天星?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿所有的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按着一个节拍前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装上的不是钻石呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你的红心!"}]}